<item>
            <title>[LU-10379] &quot;lfs changelog&quot; generates constant &quot;Changelog: Input/output error&quot; errors</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10379</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m seeing lots of errors from &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lfs changelog&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; and &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lfs changelog_clear&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; commands:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/70f5331a-db46-11e7-a066-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/70f5331a-db46-11e7-a066-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;verifying changelog mask
CMD: trevis-13vm4 /usr/sbin/lctl set_param mdd.*.changelog_mask=-MKDIR
CMD: trevis-13vm4 /usr/sbin/lctl set_param mdd.*.changelog_mask=-CLOSE
CMD: trevis-13vm4 /usr/sbin/lctl set_param mdd.*.changelog_mask=+MKDIR
CMD: trevis-13vm4 /usr/sbin/lctl set_param mdd.*.changelog_mask=+CLOSE
Changelog: Input/output error
lustre-MDT0000.7 01CREAT 11:20:48.951746235 2017.12.07 0x0 t=[0x200002b12:0x89c:0x0] j=cp.0 ef=0x0 p=[0x200002b12:0x89a:0x0] pic1.jpg
lustre-MDT0000.8 11CLOSE 11:20:48.955294645 2017.12.07 0xc2 t=[0x200002b12:0x89c:0x0] j=cp.0 ef=0x0
:
Changelog: Input/output error
Changelog: Input/output error
verifying target fid
Changelog: Input/output error
verifying parent fid
Changelog: Input/output error
getting records for cl1
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This doesn&apos;t &lt;em&gt;appear&lt;/em&gt; to be affecting functionality, but makes these commands difficult to use.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
