                            <comment id="216240" author="adilger" created="Thu, 14 Dec 2017 00:17:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It may be that this problem is fixed by &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10267&quot; title=&quot;Wrong poll() returned revents for changelog device&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-10267&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-10267&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, and I suspect it may have been introduced by &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10218&quot; title=&quot;errors not propagated to changelog readers&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-10218&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-10218&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.  Filed this bug in case it has a different cause, because I don&apos;t think we should release 2.11 with this problem.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
